OL,3,CHS2 an example of 'how not to run a
OL,4,Cmajor project', report finds
OL,6,FAn influential group of MPs has warned
OL,7,Fthat HS2 is an example of "how not to
OL,8,Frun a major project" says and the
OL,9,FGovernment "must not waste" its latest
OL,10,Fopportunity to reset the programme.
OL,12,FThe Department for Transport (DfT) has
OL,13,F"failed in its oversight and financial
OL,14,Fcontrol" of the scheme, the Commons
OL,15,FPublic Accounts Committee (PAC) said.
OL,17,FThe cross-party group of MPs warned
OL,18,Fthere is "a reputational risk to the
OL,19,FUK" because of the project.
