OL,6,FIn its damning report, the PAC said
OL,7,FHS2 Ltd ` the Government-owned company
OL,8,Fresponsible for building the high-
OL,9,Fspeed railway ` and the DfT have
OL,10,F"failed to work together effectively".
OL,12,FThis is "starkly illustrated by their
OL,13,Fcontinued disagreement" over how much
OL,14,Fit will cost to build the line from
OL,15,FLondon to the West Midlands, it stated.
