OL,4,Cmajor project', report finds
OL,6,FThe DfT's estimated range in November
OL,7,F2023 was #45 billion to #54 billion,
OL,8,Fwhile HS2 Ltd's latest estimate in
OL,9,FJune 2024 was between #54 billion and
OL,10,F#66 billion. All these figures were in
OL,11,F2019 prices.Once adjusted for
OL,12,Finflation, the cost "might be close to
OL,13,F#80 billion", according to the report.
OL,15,FThe PAC said: "The HS2 programme has
OL,16,Fbecome a casebook example of how not
OL,17,Fto run a major project.
