OL,6,F"It is unacceptable that over a decade
OL,7,Finto the programme we still do not
OL,8,Fknow what it will cost, what the final
OL,9,Fscope will be, when it will finally be
OL,10,Fcompleted or what benefits it will
OL,11,Fdeliver."
OL,13,FShortly after joining HS2 Ltd as chief
OL,14,Fexecutive at the start of December
OL,15,F2024, Mark Wild said the project was
OL,16,F"in a very serious situation that
OL,17,Frequires a fundamental reset".
