OL,6,FIn October last year, the former prime
OL,7,Fminister Rishi Sunak cancelled a plan
OL,8,Fto extend HS2 between the West
OL,9,FMidlands and Manchester.
OL,11,FThe original plans were in three
OL,12,Fphases:
OL,14,FPhase 1: London Euston to Birmingham
OL,15,FCurzon Street, with intermediate
OL,16,Fstations at Old Oak Common in the
OL,17,Fwestern suburbs and at Birmingham
OL,18,FAirport.
