OL,6,FPhase 2A: To extend the line from
OL,7,FFradley in the West Midlands to Crewe
OL,8,Fin Cheshire.
OL,10,FPhase 2B: An eastern leg from the West
OL,11,FMidlands to the East Midlands and a
OL,12,Fwestern leg from Crewe to Manchester.
OL,14,FThe planned leg to Leeds was axed in
OL,15,FNovember 2021 and phase 2 was later
OL,16,Fcancelled too.
OL,18,FA previous review was carried out in
OL,19,F2020 because of escalating costs and
OL,20,Fdelays.
